meta.title: Solr development site : News Introduction
meta.description: Exports news records for news extension
meta.notes:
Exports the news data to news.xml file.
The exported data should be moved to packages/introduction_news/Initialisation/ and named data.xml and data.xml.files also following command could be used: ``` mv public/fileadmin/user_upload/_temp_/importexport/news.xml packages/introduction_news/Initialisation/data.xml mv public/fileadmin/user_upload/_temp_/importexport/news.xml.files packages/introduction_news/Initialisation/data.xml.files ```
